cyacq extends tender for cyclops cyl cyacq corp said it extended its dlr a share tender offer for cyclops corp to march from today cyacq was formed by citicorp capital investors ltd and audio video affiliates inc ava to acquire cyclops the tender offer began on february six the offer is conditioned upon at least pct of the outstanding shares and at least pct of the voting securities being tendered before expiration of the offer as of march six only shares of cyclops mln outstanding shares had been tendered reuter 